sk|s|nt|Dalthor, North, dealt and passed and Ladybird, East, opened with a weak 2@S. What call do you think Fred made as South? Both sides were vulnerable (you can tell this by the graphic in the top left corner above - red means vulnerable) and the game was being scored as IMP pairs.|
