nt|In this deal we have seen 2 examples of what the ^*Bloser on loser^*N play can accomplish. First, this technique was used to ^*Brectify the count^*N for a ^*Bsqueeze^*N. Second, this tecnique was used like a ^*Bthrown in^*N for an ^*Bendplay^*N (except in this deal the defender had been ^*ithrown in^*N already). There are a lot of other ways that the ^*Bloser on loser^*N play can win tricks for you. Be on the lookout for them!|
